data.description: SUBSTANTIAL PRICE REDUCTION! Welcome to this spacious two-story home on a quiet cul-de-sac in The Preserve at Pecan Creek. The flexible floor plan is sure to meet your family's needs! The kitchen has granite counters, painted cabinets, SS appliances, an eating nook and breakfast bar open to the living room that features a soaring ceiling, lots of natural light, and a gas log fireplace. The front entry has the dining room on one side and a flex room that could be used as an office, play room or living room on the other. The secluded primary bedroom and ensuite bath, utility room and half-bath are all downstairs. Engineered wood and tile flooring throughout the first floor. Upstairs you'll find the media room, a separate living or game room, three bedrooms with walk-in closets, and a full bath. Great location in a planned community with many amenities, close to I-35, shopping, schools, restaurants and entertainment.
